hopobject.body: I work with computers how much do cancer drugs cost UK fitness chain Gymbox just launched its new class dubbed Playboy Bunny Bootcamp, which is "inspired by the confidence, health and zest for life of the Playboy Bunnies who made the Playboy Clubs famous for more than 50 years." What it entails: a 45-minute high-intensity workout designed to have you not only looking fit should you don a bunny costume but feeling "healthy and empowered."
